@startuml
!theme plain
title Consistency Problem: Update Cache First, then DB

actor "Request A" as A
actor "Request B" as B
entity "Cache" as Cache
database "Database" as DB

A -> Cache : Update cache to 1
B -> Cache : Update cache to 2
B -> DB : Update DB to 2
A -> DB : Update DB to 1

note over A, DB #LightPink
**Result: Cache = 2, DB = 1 -> Data inconsistency**
end note

@enduml